snippet.title: Spice and Wolf Opening Videogame "My One Year with Holo"
snippet.description:
Hello everyone.
This is my first video. Hope you all like it. The video portrayed is the opening for the Spice and Wolf DS game "My One Year with Holo". I do not own any of these images, video nor audio. The song name is "Tonari ni Iru yo" and it belongs to its proper owners including the artist: Koshimizu Ami.
